**Summary:** Documents the Experiment Management API holdout group endpoints for Amplitude Experiment, including GET /api/1/holdouts for listing holdout groups, GET /api/1/holdouts/<id> for retrieving details, PATCH /api/1/holdouts/{id} for editing, and POST /api/1/holdouts for creating new holdout groups with configuration options like holdoutPercentage, evaluationMode, bucketingKey, and experiment associations.

